        "description": "The dataset was retrieved from Open Data Telangana, from February 1, 2023, to January 31, 2025 with daily granularity. The dataset contains various fields such as District, Mandal, Date, rainfall (in millimeters), minimum and maximum temperature (in Celsius), minimum and maximum wind speed, and humidity. It provides a District and Mandal wise distribution as well.\n\nTotal Rows - 4,45,213\nTotal Columns - 10\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nColumn Descriptors\nDistrict\n- Name of District (String)\nMandal\n- Name of Mandal (String)\nDate\n- Date (String)\nRain (mm)\n- Rainfall as measured in millimeters (Float)\nMin Temp (\u00b0C)\n- Minimum Temperature as measured in Celsius (Float)\nMax Temp (\u00b0C)\n- Maximum Temperature as measured in Celsius (Float)\nMin Humidity (%)\n- Minimum Humidity as measured in Percentage (Float)\nMax Humidity (%)\n- Maximum Humidity as measured in Percentage (Float)\nMin Wind Speed (Kmph)\n- Minimum Windspeed as measured in Kmph (Float)\nMax Wind Speed (Kmph)\n- Maximum Windspeed as measured in Kmph (Float)\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nDistrict: Name of District (String)\nMandal: Name of Mandal (String)\nDate: Date (String)\nRain (mm): Rainfall as measured in millimeters (Float)\nMin Temp (\u00b0C): Minimum Temperature as measured in Celsius (Float)\nMax Temp (\u00b0C): Maximum Temperature as measured in Celsius (Float)\nMin Humidity (%): Minimum Humidity as measured in Percentage (Float)\nMax Humidity (%): Maximum Humidity as measured in Percentage (Float)\nMin Wind Speed (Kmph): Minimum Windspeed as measured in Kmph (Float)\nMax Wind Speed (Kmph): Maximum Windspeed as measured in Kmph (Float)\n",
